  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create an illusion of yourself throwing a ball of elementally charged Chakra that explodes for 1d4 damage per two levels, up to 5d4, of an elemental type of your choice. This damage is not affected by energy resistances, but creatures immune to the element will be unaffected by the technique. The damage cannot bring creatures below 0 HP, but those reduced to 0 HP will remain @Condition[unconscious]{unconscious} for 1d4+2 minutes or until healed.<br><br>Creatures without use of their sense of sight, smell, touch and hearing are immune to this illusion as well, and creatures warned about its effects gain a +8 bonus on their save to resist it (identifying does not grant this bonus).</p>\n\n\n\n",
